@startuml B8 Follow-up Operator Feedback and E2E
title B8 Follow-up - Operator Feedback, Merge Outcome Refinement, Real-Org E2E

actor "Board Operator" as Board
actor "Agent" as Agent

rectangle "Issue Retrieval Run" as Retrieval
database "retrieval_feedback_events" as Feedback
database "retrieval_role_profiles" as Profiles
rectangle "Multi-hop Graph Traversal\nmaxDepth=2" as Graph
rectangle "Merge Candidate Resolution" as Merge
rectangle "Follow-up Issue Retrieval" as Followup

Agent --> Retrieval
Board --> Feedback : operator_pin / operator_hide
Merge --> Feedback : merged / rejected
Feedback --> Profiles
Profiles --> Followup
Graph --> Followup
Agent --> Followup

note right of Graph
- two-hop limit
- edge decay
- edge-type weighted traversal
end note

note bottom of Followup
E2E success signal:
- graphHitCount > 0
- personalization.applied = true
- personalizedHitCount > 0
end note

@enduml
